{"tid":2500904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙嘴海面發現浮屍，警員進行調查，初步認為案件“有可疑”。","createTime":"2021-04-23T04:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T06:28:10.000Z","uid":396262,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c5481e0bb665abb3b748b340b853ffe1a10c6126","tid":2500904,"uid":396262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTixHSnriJx9cz8U9N1xNoDyzEGs37n4JfYSyfo2WKQjF?filename=Q1ESqoi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ1ESqoi.png&h=54a1c201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRaNygFKh8e3ZHq5HSXgggNydyVqLAiVwW2Ay18GCLB88?filename=yrSQb3H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrSQb3H.png&h=7cb14216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVTgd5ru2ekvHEh68w331eyJrqfkL1dgFekqGHBfAvncC?filename=yBMYkW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyBMYkW5.jpg&h=937007a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴海面發現浮屍，早上6時許，天星碼頭對開海面，路經船家發現海面有一具男子浮屍，大驚立刻報警，消防及水警趕至現場，稍後撈起屍體送返碼頭，警員進行調查，發現屍體頭部有傷痕腳部纏有一個袋，初步認為案件有可疑，召探員到場作深入調查。<br />\n經初步調查，死者為一名早前失蹤的長者，身上有證件、門匙、金錢、金鏈及一張濕透的字條，雙腳纏上一條繩，另一端則綁有一個旅行袋，袋內裝有相信是磚塊的重物，頭部傷勢不排除由船槳所做成，死因有待法醫檢驗，死者屍體由仵工移送殮房。"},{"pid":"8dee5d27ec2857f38c955654de9e1c6c26867816","tid":2500904,"uid":3457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"幾時會火化條屍？"},{"pid":"0ed47ad21d7b184c0e3b4f60c7731a7749dc182e","tid":2500904,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"唔多膽講幾多歳"},{"pid":"e66a5d38712216df60157223250837d6d8b807ea","tid":2500904,"uid":39167,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"依單一定唔係黑警做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a83036515fb1d61410b0c9d02d0